    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride? I'm parting with my absolute favorite car, and it's in really lovely shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me and still looks fantastic cruising down the street. It's been well-loved and is totally ready for its next owner to take it on some fun adventures. I've taken great care of it, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. Suspension components maintain factory geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and communicative feedback expected of the E46's MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain is robust, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a clean oil analysis. This is a driver-focused example optimized for longitudinal and lateral performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. Ready for sale.",
      "price": 28000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is a sophisticated executive sedan that perfectly balances performance and comfort. The exterior is finished in a striking Bluestone Metallic that still holds a deep, mirror-like shine. While the body is straight and free of major dents, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the edge of the rear passenger-side alloy wheel, consistent with respectful road use. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather interior is exceptionally clean; the seats are firm and supportive, with only very light wear visible on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All cabin technology, including the 10.2-inch iDrive touchscreen, navigation, and the premium Harman Kardon sound system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having followed a strict factory maintenance schedule. Within the last 3,000 miles, it has received a comprehensive multi-point inspection, a fresh oil service, and new brake pads. The turbocharged inline-six engine runs smoothly and delivers power effortlessly through the xDrive all-wheel-drive system. This is a reliable, well-documented vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection by our expert technicians, this automobile offers a superior driving experience and represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning buyer seeking reliability without compromise. This unit remains in commendable condition, prepared for immediate delivery and long-term service.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been so well-loved and is in great shape. It drives super smooth and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and it's honestly such a joy to be behind the wheel. Perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, an engineering marvel featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers a linear 333 hp to the rear wheels through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M Differential Lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads, and the VANOS system has been overhauled for optimal cam timing. The chassis retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, providing the communicative feedback and balance typical of this high-revving platform. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and throttle response.",
